    "storyId": "00000021086001",
    "title": "0",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "先日、姉様の絵をご覧になった方から\n言伝を頼まれました。\n『うちの画廊に置かせてもらえないか』と。",
            "enText": "A few days ago, a person that saw your \npainting left a message for you. \nThey said \"Could we please put it in our art \ngallery?\".",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": 6499785456722061048,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロラモーヌ",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ramonu",
            "jpText": "そう――で？",
            "enText": "Really now. And?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": 8383059492280157425,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "その……『華やかで繊細な色使いが\nラモーヌさんの美しいレース愛を\n感じさせる素晴らしい作品』、とも――",
            "enText": "Uhh......They also said \"It's a wonderful \npiece that brings to mind Ramonu's beautiful \nlove for the race through the vivid and \ndelicate use of colors.\"",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": 6251373520533279128,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロラモーヌ",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ramonu",
            "jpText": "貴方はそう思っていないのね。",
            "enText": "You don't agree with them, do you?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": 8105746889808171310,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "その、私は、あの絵を…………\n――怖い、と感じてしまいました。",
            "enText": "Umm, I personally find that painting to be...... \nfrightening.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "pathId": -145585365797918388,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "見ていると……衝動に駆られるのです。\n此処にいてはいけないような、\n今すぐ駆けださなくてはいけないような――",
            "enText": "Whenever I see it......my instincts overwhelm \nme, saying that it's dangerous and I have to \nleave quickly.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "pathId": 4569791236506777178,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロラモーヌ",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ramonu",
            "jpText": "よくってよ、それで。",
            "enText": "That's fine as it is.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "pathId": 5605442503347265373,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロラモーヌ",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ramonu",
            "jpText": "あれは、捌け口。\n思慕と激情を\n油と『愛』で溶いて塗り広げたモノ。",
            "enText": "That painting was me unleashing my \nemotions. My longing and ferocity, mixed \nwith the oil paint and my \"love\", smeared \nacross the canvas.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "pathId": -8630503740745366637,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロラモーヌ",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ramonu",
            "jpText": "表層をなぞって\n『愛』を語るような輩に\n扱える代物じゃない――",
            "enText": "Such a piece shouldn't be handled by fools \nthat only look at the surface and start going \non about \"love\".",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "pathId": -158311309610850006,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "姉様……！\nはい、私もそう思います。",
            "enText": "Nee-sama......! \nYes, I completely agree.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "pathId": 6870790948333450879,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロラモーヌ",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ramonu",
            "jpText": "そう、ではその通り\n言伝、お願いね。",
            "enText": "Well then. Please relay my exact answer to \nthem.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "pathId": -4365302233431961450,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "えっ……\n姉様……！？",
            "enText": "Ehh......? \nNee-sama......!?",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "pathId": -6852763875109247767,
            "blockIdx": 12
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1703830548,
    "humanTl": true
}